We think now its better to use already provided solutions which has been proven and as we said we will always look to use strategic partners we plan to build a very wide platform divided in several sectors and we think partnering up and focusing on more important issues on the start will be the key for success. SOLUTIONS ______________   Our vision is to build a truly smart city, a city that will be a innovation in industries, which will accomplish creation of knowledge, services to the citizen our city will tend to achieve scalable solutions that take advantage of information and communications technology to increase efficiencies, reduce costs, and enhance quality of life. One of our main goal and objectives is to create a efficient city that will save resources and tend to create a easy life for its citizens, we want to provide users a social network that connects them together, also to provide them with security of their resources and after all that we want to provide them with entertainment, which will not lack in our city. Our main focus will be on the economy side of the game and we want to enable people competable marketplace with minimal fees, many options how they can spend their tokens on our platform, we have made sustainable development goals which our platform offers, so we want to provide people with security and combine two worlds old with the new in game changing platform which is created to solve some problems we face today.   HOW IT WORKS ______________  Smart City Eco is targeting all mayor global economy industries, we want to provide smart solutions based on blockchain technology and target most lucrative.
